h1 Getting Started
p BitTorious may eventually accept any BitTorrent client that supports HTTP proxies but currently uTorrent is the only officially supported client. For this reason we will use uTorrent for the examples in this tutorial. A free version of uTorrent is available at <a href=http://www.utorrent.com>utorrent.com</a>. Please note that the sample screenshots were made using the uTorrent client for Mac and consequently may look a little different for Windows users.
